ingapore%2C%20a%20sober%20clubbing%20event%20where%20matcha%20trumped%20alcohol.%3Cp%3EExposure%20Therapy%2C%20Jeegly%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20attended%20a%20matcha%20rave%20in%20Singapore%20at%20a%20nightclub%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20afternoon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHigh%20on%20strawberry%20matchas%2C%20sober%20clubbers%20partied%20hard%20to%20remixes%20of%20songs%20by%20Tyla%20and%20Bad%20Bunny.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMost%20people%20I%20spoke%20to%20said%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%20in%20bed%20by%2010%20p.m.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20heard%20about%20a%204%20to%208%20p.m.%20matcha%20party%20in%20Singapore%2C%20I%20expected%20to%20see%20millennials%20dancing%20in%20brunch%20outfits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20found%20a%20packed%20nightclub%2C%20smoke%20machines%2C%20and%20remixes%20of%20Bad%20Bunny%20and%20Tyla%20songs%20that%20were%20making%20perfectly%20sober%20clubbers%20go%20wild%20at%20%26quot%3BMatcha%20Rave%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20sober%20daytime%20clubbing%20event%20organized%20by%20Exposure%20Therapy%2C%20a%20Singaporean%20events%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223950%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sold-out%20rave%20was%20held%20in%20an%20events%20space%20in%20Singapore's%20central%20business%20district.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a56599a17a8c5b405322b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222962%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20sold-out%20rave%20was%20held%20in%20an%20events%20space%20in%20Singapore's%20central%20business%20district.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20I%20attended%20their%20second%20session%2C%20a%20sold-out%20party%20at%20Rasa%20Space%20%E2%80%94%20a%20bar%2C%20restaurant%2C%20and%20nightclub%20in%20the%20city's%20central%20business%20district.%20Tickets%20cost%2020%20Singapore%20dollars%20apiece%2C%20or%20about%20%2415.50.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20that%20ther