ok's%20is%20compulsory%20rather%20than%20optional%2C%20and%20on%20a%20quick%20timeline.%20Big%20Tech%20platforms%20are%20increasingly%20pushing%20advertisers%20to%20use%20AI-powered%20tools%20that%20create%20ads%20and%20determine%20which%20users%20to%20target%20and%20where%20to%20place%20those%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20direction%20the%20whole%20industry%20is%20moving%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Neil%20Baker%2C%20head%20of%20media%20at%20the%20digital%20ad%20agency%20TUG.%20TikTok%20offers%20a%20suite%20of%20other%20AI%20tools%20for%20advertisers%2C%20including%20options%20to%20produce%20ads%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-getting-into-murky-business-of-ai-generated-creator-ads-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-generated%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Favatars.it%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavatars.%3C%2Fa%3E%20It%20also%20offers%20Smart%2B%2C%20an%20AI%20tool%20similar%20to%20GMV%20Max%2C%20which%20automates%20and%20generates%20campaigns%20to%20achieve%20goals%20like%20video%20views%20or%20website%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAutomated%20tools%20have%20been%20a%20boon%20for%20Big%20Tech%20platforms.%20Tech%20giants%20say%20they%20save%20time%20and%20drive%20performance%20for%20advertisers.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcmo-tried-google-ai-tools-stopped-using-them-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESome%20marketers%20say%3C%2Fa%3E%20they're%20black%20boxes%20that%20strip%20them%20of%20control.%20These%20algorithms%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-boosts-ad-performance-but-some-advertisers-push-back-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edon't%20always%20offer%20a%20complete%20picture%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20which%20ads%20worked%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fipg-mediabrands-privacy-alert-pause-google-performance-max-ads-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%