0care%20less%20about%20off-platform%20tracking%2C%20and%20the%20product%20includes%20some%20guarantees%20that%20small%20sellers%20appreciate.%20For%20example%2C%20TikTok%20created%20a%20feature%20called%20%26quot%3BROI%20Protection%26quot%3B%20within%20GMV%20Max%20designed%20to%20assure%20advertisers%20that%20their%20campaigns%20would%20drive%20results.%20TikTok%20automatically%20issues%20ad%20credits%20if%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20for%20a%20particular%20campaign%20falls%20below%2090%25%20of%20the%20target%20that%20the%20advertiser%20chose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaty%20Hallam%2C%20head%20of%20client%20services%20at%20TikTok%20commerce%20specialist%20agency%20Onyx%2C%20said%20the%20tool%20has%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bgame%20changer%26quot%3B%20for%20some%20merchants'%20sales%20and%20a%20time%20saver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277935194-ae1a-4e05-8d64-b4f37cc1d21b%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20AI%20black%20box%20makes%20some%20big%20brands%20uneasy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ad%20buyers%20who%20spoke%20with%20Business%20Insider%20said%20that%20some%20large%20advertisers%20they%20work%20with%20had%20misgivings%20about%20TikTok%20Shop's%20forced%20shift.%20They%20said%20that%20TikTok%20had%20already%20moved%20the%20original%20deadline%20from%20July%20to%20September%20after%20complaints%20from%20the%20ad%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHousehold%20names%20are%20more%20hesitant%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jack%20Johnston%2C%20head%20of%20social%20innovation%20at%20the%20ad%20agency%20Tinuiti.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20very%20big%20creative%20and%20media%20strategies%2C%20and%20they%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20control%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224272%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Electronics%20seller%20Anker%20is%20a%20top%20TikTok%20Shop%20merchant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673e0c22ede4eeae39289c76%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222848%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElectronics%20seller%20Anke