20through%20their%20programmed%20arcs.%20Cameras%20direct%20sanding%20tools%20to%20paint%20blemishes.%20Uncrewed%20taxis%20move%20vehicles%20and%20parts%20to%20their%20next%20manufacturing%20destination.%20A%20four-legged%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboston-dynamics-spot-youtube-videos-future-robots-marc-raibert-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBoston%20Dynamics%20AI%20dog%20named%20Spot%3C%2Fa%3E%20walks%20through%20the%20facility%20and%20scans%20components%20to%20ensure%20they're%20snapped%20into%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20facility%2C%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhyundai-metaplant-georgia-us-ev-factory-tour-photos-see-inside-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHyundai%20Motor%20Group%20Metaplant%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20roughly%20equivalent%20to%20278%20football%20fields%20and%20comes%20with%20a%20nearly%20%247.6%20billion%20price%20tag%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HMGMA%20facility%2C%20which%20celebrated%20its%20grand%20opening%20in%20March%2C%20puts%20Hyundai%20in%20a%20unique%20position%20compared%20to%20other%20automakers.%20While%20most%20US%20automakers%20are%20retrofitting%20decade-old%20plants%20with%20AI%20and%20robotics%2C%20Hyundai%20built%20HMGMA%20from%20the%20ground%20up%20with%20AI%2C%20Nvidia%20chips%2C%20and%20robotics%20at%20its%20core.%20Each%20vehicle%20built%20in%20the%20plant%20%E2%80%94%20including%20cars%20in%20all%20three%20of%20Hyundai%20Motor%20Group's%20brands%20%E2%80%94%20runs%20through%20at%20least%2023%20AI-based%20or%20robotic%20systems%20before%20it's%20finalized%2C%20according%20to%20Hyundai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20analysts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Hyundai's%20AI-first%20approach%20could%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20navigating%20policy%20changes%20and%20customer%20trends%20that%20impact%20the%20carmaker's%20bottom%20line.%20The%20technology%20can%20help%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-uses-ai-cameras-in-factories-prevent-recalls-costly-rework-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimprove%20quality%20control%20measures%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20reduce%20manufacturing%20costs%20in%20ways%20that%20traditional%20manufacturing%20can't%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHyundai's%20integration%20of%20humanoid%20robots%20and%20such%20sets%20a%20new%20benchmark%20for%20smart%20manufacturing%2C%26quot%3B%20Erin%20Keating%2C%20an%20executive%20analyst%20at%20Cox%20Automotive%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BPotentially%2C%20there%20are%20cost%20savings%2C%20and%20it%20likely%20offers%20the%20ability%20for%20Hyundai%20and%20others%20to%20respond%20faster%20to%20any%20industrial%20disruption.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbf3c1c0-767f-4641-8c1e-a720b0fabcf9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20isn't%20replacing%20Hyundai's%20workforce%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20center%20of%20Hyundai's%20Georgia%20operation%20is%20an%20integrated%20digital%20command%20hub%20that%20acts%20as%20a%20digital%20twin%2C%20or%20a%20computer%20simulation%20that%20mirrors%20the%20physical%20plant%20in%20real%20time%2C%20said%20Miles%20Johnson%2C%20Hyundai's%20communications%20representative%20for%20its%20electric-powered%20Ioniq-brand%20vehicles%20and%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fartificial-intelligence-robotics-predictive-maintenance-manufacturing-factory-solutions-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESensors%20collect%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20across%20the%20production%20floor%2C%20then%20an%20AI%20algorithm%20creates%20a%20virtual%20replica%20of%20each%20step%20in%20the%20real-life%20manufacturing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20can%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20predicting%20optimized%20outcomes%20and%20identifying%20root%20causes%20of%20production%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20quality%20issue%20arises%20in%20production%2C%20the%20AI%20system%20can%20search%20past%20data%20it%20has%20been%20trained%20on%20to%20identify%20the%20likely%20cause%20and%20suggest%20a%20corrective%20action%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeating%20said%20that%20Hyundai's%20AI%20can%20help%20%26quot%3Bdetect%20defects%20in%20real%20time%2C%20analyze%20root%20causes%2C%20and%20suggest%20corrective%20actions%20that%20can%20significantly%20reduce%20rework%2C%20scrap%2C%20and%20warranty%20claims.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brand's%20two%20retro-modern%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-vehicles-evs-were-excited-to-test-drive-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eelectric%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Ioniq%205%20and%20Ioniq%209%20SUVs%2C%20are%20built%20with%20these%20highly%20technical%20processes.%20The%20plant%20will%20eventually%20serve%20Hyundai's%20other%20brands%20as%20well%3B%20Kia%20production%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20in%202026%2C%20with%20Genesis%20vehicles%20planned%20for%20an%20unspecified%20future%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%2C%20Hyundai%20said%20that%20the%20AI%20and%20robotics%20systems%20will%20assist%20humans%2C%20who%20will%20remain%20in%20charge%20of%20on-the-ground%20robotics%20maintenance%2C%20data%20analysis%2C%20and%20parts%20installation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20roles%20now%20involve%20programming%20the%20factory's%20850%20robots%2C%20troubleshooting%20AI%2C%20or%20interpreting%20production%20data%20rather%20than%20performing%20repetitive%20physical%20tasks.%20The%20company%20aims%20to%20hire%208%2C500%20employees%20at%20HMGMA%20by%202031%20and%20has%20dubbed%20the%20project%20the%20largest%20single%20business%20investment%20in%20Georgia's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20Hyundai%20said%20it%20had%20already%20hired%201%2C000%20full-time%20staff%20members%20at%20the%20plant.%20The%20company%20also%20built%20a%20nearby%20Hyundai%20Mobility%20Training%20Center%20of%20Georgia%2C%20where%20it%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupply-chain-courses-at-universities-preparing-students-for-ai-technology-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrain%20a%20pipeline%20of%20college-level%20talent%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20plant.%20The%20program%2C%20which%20is%20in%20coordination%20with%20three%20local%20technical%20colleges%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20open%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d09719f-e570-4d4a-94f5-529ae7e71719%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20could%20help%20carmakers%20with%20cost%20management%20and%20supply-chain%20disruptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHyundai's%20massive%20AI%20investment%20faces%20significant%20challenges%20in%20the%20current%20automotive%20market.%20Both%20the%20Ioniq%205%20and%20Ioniq%209%20were%20positioned%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20then-President%20Joe%20Biden's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-heres-whats-in-the-manchin-deal-for-bidens-agenda-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EInflation%20Reduction%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20cars%20are%20both%20eligible%20for%20the%20%247%2C500%20tax%20credits%20for%20EVs%20assembled%20in%20American%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Americans'%20uptake%20of%20EVs%20has%20underperformed%20analysts'%20predictions%20since%20Hyundai%20broke%20ground%20on%20HMGMA%20in%20October%202022.%20Now%2C%20EV%20adoption%20is%20facing%20more%20federal%20pushback%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fall-the-evs-set-to-lose-the-federal-tax-credit-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esubsidies%20for%20EVs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20set%20to%20end%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHyundai%20is%20now%20betting%20that%20its%20EVs%2C%20including%20the%20three-row%20Ioniq%209%2C%20which%20launched%20in%20May%202025%2C%20will%20attract%20buyers%20without%20the%20need%20for%20tax%20incentives.%20However%2C%20some%20industry%20analysts%20say%20that%20Hyundai's%20AI-powered%20manufacturing%20can%20still%20