%5C%22%3Etrain%20rides%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20over%20seven%20hours%2C%20I%20knew%20I'd%20be%20eating%20a%20meal%20on%20both%20journeys.%20For%20my%20trip%20from%20New%20York%20City%20to%20Rochester%2C%20it%20was%20lunch%2C%20and%20I%20got%20a%20surprisingly%20good%20salad%20and%20a%20bag%20of%20chips%20from%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20my%20surprise%2C%20though%2C%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20car%20closed%20for%20an%20hour%20of%20the%20journey%2C%20which%20would%20have%20been%20a%20problem%20if%20I%20had%20timed%20my%20lunch%20incorrectly%20or%20wanted%20a%20snack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20aware%20I%20can%20get%20hangry%2C%20so%20for%20my%20return%20trip%2C%20I%20packed%20some%20Cheez-Its%20as%20a%20backup%20snack%20in%20case%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20closure%20coincided%20with%20my%20hunger.%20The%20caf%C3%A9%20car%20is%20a%20benefit%20of%20Amtrak%2C%20but%20I'd%20recommend%20bringing%20additional%20snacks%20in%20case%20it's%20unavailable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20biggest%20mistake%20was%20booking%20a%20train%20with%20a%20long%20stop.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20seflie%20of%20a%20woman%20in%20front%20of%20an%20Amtrak%20sign%20that%20says%20%26quot%3BAlbany-Rensselaer%2C%20NY.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683e01adca50259add4d7807%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Pettyjohn%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20New%20York%20City%20early%20on%20a%20Thursday%20and%20planned%20to%20return%20on%20Friday%20afternoon%2C%20giving%20myself%20time%20to%20do%20some%20sightseeing%20in%20the%20morning%20before%20I%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20focused%20on%20departure%20time%20instead%20of%20arrival%20time%20for%20my%20return%2C%20not%20noticing%20until%20after%20I%20booked%20my%20ticket%20that%20the%20trip%20back%20would%20take%20nine%20hours%20instead%20of%20the%20seven%20it%20took%20to%20get%20to%20Rochester.%20I%20thought%20maybe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-to-improve-long-train-rides-tips-frequent-amtrak-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20train%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20just%20be%20making%20more%20stops%2C%20but%20it%20actually%20made%20an%20extended%20stop%20in%20Albany%20for%20over%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20to%20connect%20with%20another%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pause%2C%20the%20lights%20were%20off%2C%20the%20AC%20only%20came%20on%20sporadically%2C%20and%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20car%20was%20closed.%20I%20was%20frustrated%20when%20I%20realized%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20but%20I%20had%20no%20one%20to%20blame%20but%20myself.%20Amtrak%20had%20clearly%20listed%20the%20estimated%20arrival%20time%20on%20my%20ticket%20when%20I%20purchased%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20the%20most%20of%20the%20time%20we%20were%20stopped%2C%20grabbing%20a%20lackluster%20dinner%20from%20a%20small%20caf%C3%A9%20at%20the%20Albany%20station%20and%20walking%20around%20to%20stretch%20my%20legs.%20It%20wasn't%20a%20huge%20problem%20in%20the%20grand%20scheme%20of%20things%2C%20but%20next%20time%2C%20I'll%20pay%20closer%20attention%20to%20journey%20length%20when%20booking%20my%20Amtrak%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20sounds%20silly%2C%20but%20I%20should%20have%20been%20more%20careful%20with%20my%20body%20as%20I%20got%20used%20to%20being%20on%20a%20train.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20woman%20sitting%20on%20a%20train.%20It's%20dark%20outside%20in%20the%20nearby%20window.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a486d2cfc04e97619ba006%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Pettyjohn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20pretty%20clumsy%20person%20by%20nature%2C%20prone%20to%20tripping%20and%20lacking%20basic%20hand-eye%20coordination.%3C%2Fp%3E%