rom%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20liked%20its%20slower%20pace%20of%20life%2C%20which%20didn't%20seem%20all%20about%20work.%20I%20feel%20like%20in%20the%20US%2C%20people%20live%20to%20work%2C%20whereas%20in%20Spain%2C%20they%20work%20to%20live%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cspan%3Epeople%20here%20aren't%20responding%20to%20emails%20at%209%20p.m.%2C%20outside%20their%20work%20hours.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20idea%20of%20a%20calmer%2C%20more%20relaxed%20way%20of%20life%20was%20really%20appealing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20living%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-traveling-to-phoenix-arizona%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edowntown%20Phoenix%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20a%20part%20of%20the%20city%20that%20felt%20progressive.%20Still%2C%20outside%20that%20bubble%2C%20it%20was%20very%20conservative%2C%20which%20was%20concerning%20to%20me%20as%20a%20queer%20woman.%20I%20was%20also%20uneasy%20about%20the%20strong%20gun%20culture%20in%20Arizona%2C%20and%20I%20always%20felt%20stuck%20in%20fight-or-flight%20mode.%20I%20wanted%20to%20live%20somewhere%20that%20felt%20less%20stressful%20and%20safer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20more%20than%20a%20year%20of%20planning%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20job%2C%20sold%20my%20car%2C%20my%20townhouse%2C%20and%20almost%20everything%20else%20I%20owned%2C%20and%20headed%20to%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2260cc31bb-51c7-451a-9adc-1f9be7744a22%5C%22%3EI%20passed%20up%20Barcelona%20for%20M%C3%A1laga%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20moving%2C%20I%20did%20as%20much%20research%20as%20I%20could%2C%20but%20I%20was%20still%20nervous%20getting%20on%20that%20plane%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20it%20would%20be%20crazy%20to%20make%20that%20kind%20of%20move%20without%20being%20nervous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20my%20concerns%20about%20moving%20weren't%20as%20big%20as%20my%20reasons%20for%20wanting%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrities-who-left-usa-political-rea