p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20expect%20that%20this%20is%20a%20message%20Powell%20will%20reinforce%20in%20his%20keynote%20address%20at%20the%20Jackson%20Hole%20Symposium%20on%20Friday%2C%20likely%20disappointing%20numerous%20doves%20in%20the%20market%2C%20who%20have%20bumped%20up%20the%20odds%20on%20a%20September%20cut%20to%20as%20high%20as%2085%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfit%20taking%20after%20a%20blistering%20summer%20rally%2C%20as%20well%20as%20weak%20seasonality%20have%20also%20been%20blamed%20for%20the%20two-day%20decline%20among%20chip%20and%20AI%20stocks.%20August%20and%20September%20are%20historically%20the%20weakest%20months%20of%20the%20year%20for%20the%20stock%20market.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20note%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20UBS%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20some%20alarm%20in%20the%20AI%20space%20may%20have%20been%20triggered%20by%20a%20note%20from%20MIT%20that%20said%2095%25%20of%20firms%20surveyed%20said%20they've%20seen%20no%20measurable%20return%20from%20AI%20investment%20to%20date.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESam%20Altman's%20talk%20of%20an%20AI%20bubble%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-superintelligence-labs-reorg-alexandr-wang-memo-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMeta's%20restructuring%20of%20its%20AI%20teams%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20also%20spurred%20some%20reassessment%20of%20the%20AI%20boom%20in%20recent%20days.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStill%2C%20sources%20said%20this%20week's%20drop%20shouldn't%20derail%20the%20broader%20tech%20trade%20going%20forward.%20Rate%20cuts%20will%20still%20ultimately%20be%20bullish%20for%20the%20space%20even%20as%20fears%20percolate%20that%20a%20broader%20stock%20rally%20could%20come%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20tech.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20alarmed%20by%20anything.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20kind%20of%20a%20natural%20progr