a.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171712.845-1755172127-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-487200%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EQwilt%20was%20a%20small%20moment%20with%20a%20vision%20to%20save%20a%20missing%20craft%2C%20a%20fading%20tradition%2C%20and%20a%20family%20memory%20they%20did%20not%20want%20to%20lose%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20sister%2C%20Dr%20Manasi%2C%20though%20immersed%20in%20her%20demanding%20medical%20studies%2C%20remains%20a%20core%20sounding%20board.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20brainstorm%20with%20anyone%20else%20the%20way%20I%20can%20with%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20Atharva%20says.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20smallest%20idea%20from%20her%20sparks%20something%20bigger%20in%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20those%20values%20stitched%20into%20their%20upbringing%2C%20the%20siblings%20began%20to%20see%20the%20absence%20of%20quilting%20not%20just%20as%20a%20loss%20of%20a%20family%20tradition%2C%20but%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20revive%20it%20for%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20Atharva%2C%20still%20a%20school%20student%20and%20passionate%20about%20STEM%2C%20teamed%20up%20with%20Manasi%20to%20start%20%E2%80%98Qwilt%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20grassroots%20initiative%20that%20collects%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F443759%2Fminimal-waste-wedding-chennai-uma-ram-sustainable-ideas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscarded%20clothes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20trains%20underprivileged%20women%20in%20quilting%2C%20and%20donates%20the%20finished%20quilts%20to%20orphanages%20and%20vulnerable%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBreathing%20life%20into%20a%20fading%20craft%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20previous%20neighbourhood%20of%20Dahisar%2C%20quilting%20was%20a%20familiar%20%3Cem%3Eghar%20udyog%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20home-based%20livelihood%20for%20many%20women.%20But%20after%20moving%2C%20they%20found%20the%20craft%20had%20almost%20disappeared%20from%20the%20community%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtharva%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20replacing%20the%20quilt.%20It%20was%20about%20reviving%20a%20dying%20tradition%2C%20reducing%20clothing%20waste%2C%20and%20creating%20something%20meaningful.%20We%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20circular%20model.%20People%20donate%20old%20%3Cem%3Esarees%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20bedsheets%2C%20and%20fabric.%20We%20teach%20women%20to%20make%20quilts%2C%20and%20then%20we%20gift%20those%20quilts%20to%20those%20who%20need%20them%20most.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171512.339-1755171930.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Currently%2C%2010%20women%20are%20actively%20engaged%20in%20quilting%20as%20part%20of%20Qwilt.%20They%20are%20compensated%20on%20a%20per-quilt%20basis%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171512.339-1755171930.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171512.339-1755171930-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171512.339-1755171930-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171512.339-1755171930-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171512.339-1755171930-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-487198%5C%22%20h