20persisted.%20It%20grew%20into%20an%20exhaustion%20that%20impaired%20him%20from%20completing%20even%20functional%20daily%20tasks.%20%E2%80%9CI%20just%20felt%20tired%20all%20the%20time%3B%20even%20if%20I%20ate%20well%2C%20even%20if%20I%20rested%2C%20I%20was%20tired.%20There%20came%20a%20time%20when%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20walk%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varun%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Deepa%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20his%20playing%20that%20was%20affected%3B%20whatever%20it%20was%20%E2%80%94%20it%20impacted%20his%20life.%20He%20constantly%20ran%20a%20fever%2C%20and%20his%20legs%20would%20swell.%E2%80%9D%20But%20they%20shrugged%20it%20off%20as%20something%20that%20would%20%E2%80%9Cget%20better%E2%80%9D%20until%20one%20day%20Varun%20had%20to%20be%20rushed%20to%20emergency%20care.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Saumil%20Gaur%2C%20a%20paediatric%20nephrologist%20at%20the%20Rainbow%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Hospital%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20recalls%20his%20first%20impression%20of%20Varun%20six%20years%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CVarun%20was%20very%20sick%20when%20I%20met%20him%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20He%20was%20very%20weak%3B%20his%20bones%20were%20weak%2C%20and%20they%20were%20bending.%20His%20blood%20pressure%20was%20high%2C%20and%20he%20was%20having%20seizures%20and%20was%20almost%20in%20a%20coma.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Dr%20Saumil%20and%20the%20team%20soon%20discovered%2C%20Varun%20was%20battling%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F373563%2Fvitus-care-renal-care-dialysis-tier-2-cities-chronic-kidney-disease-prabhat-shrivastava%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20silent%20form%20of%20kidney%20failure%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20battery%20of%20tests%20diagnosed%20him%20with%20Chronic%20Kidney%20Disease%20(CKD).%20The%20condition%20impairs%20the%20kidneys%E2%80%99%20ability%20to%20filter%20blood%20effectively%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20buildup%20of%20waste%20and%20excess%20fluid%20in%20the%20body.%20In%20the%20weeks%20that%20followed%2C%20the%20then%20nine-year-old%20was%20put%20on%20haemodialysis%20and%20underwent%20a%20kidney%20transplant%3B%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20kidney%20proved%20a%20perfect%20match.%20Varun%20was%20nervous%20about%20how%20the%20transplant%20would%20change%20his%20life%2C%20uncertain%20about%20whether%20it%20would%20confine%20him%20to%20the%20stands%20when%20all%20he%20wanted%20was%20to%20be%20on%20the%20field%20playing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-4-1755520798.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varun%20and%20his%20mother%20Deepa%20(L)%3B%20Varun%20won%20gold%20in%20table%20tennis%20at%20the%20World%20Transplant%20Games%202023%20(R)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-4-1755520798.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-4-1755520798-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-4-1755520798-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-4-1755520798-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-4-1755520798-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-488541%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVarun%20and%20his%20mother%20Deepa%20(L)%3B%20Varun%20won%20gold%20in%20table%20tennis%20at%20the%20World%20Transplant%20Games%202023%20(R)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%202023%2C%20at%20the%20World%20Transplant%20Games%20in%20Perth%2C%20his%20un