0there%20is%20also%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F398655%2Fdr-taru-jindal-doctor-improving-bihar-healthcare-district-hospital-maternal-care%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%20infrastructure%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20made%20conducive%20to%20the%20transplants.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20released%20by%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20(2025)%2C%20only%2013%2C476%20kidney%20transplants%20were%20performed%2C%20both%20in%20government%20and%20private%20hospitals%2C%20against%20the%20recommended%201%20lakh%20cases%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-2-1755520502.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varun%20Anand%20at%20the%20World%20Transplant%20Games%202023%3B%20he%20believes%20that%20sports%20can%20help%20one%20discover%20their%20strength%20after%20a%20transplant%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-2-1755520502.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-2-1755520502-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-2-1755520502-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-2-1755520502-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-2-1755520502-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-488535%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVarun%20Anand%20at%20the%20World%20Transplant%20Games%202023%3B%20he%20believes%20that%20sports%20can%20help%20one%20discover%20their%20strength%20after%20a%20transplant%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20revealed%20that%20the%20organ%20transplantation%20programme%20in%20the%20country%20has%20been%20crippled%20by%20multiple%20issues%2C%20especially%20insufficient%20funding%2C%20a%20shortage%20of%20specialised%20doctors%2C%20and%20procedural%20delays.%20Shortage%20of%20Intensive%20Care%20Unit%20(ICU)%20beds%20and%20lack%20of%20financial%20support%20to%20patients%20who%20require%20lifelong%20medication%20seem%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20bottlenecks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20detection%20and%20screening%20might%20help%20bridge%20the%20chasms%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F141684%2Fkamal-shahs-medical-problem-inspired-him-entrepreneur-nephroplus-dialysis%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorgan%20transplantation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20where%20ORGAN%20India%20comes%20in.%20By%20catalysing%20continued%20dialogue%20on%20the%20legal%20and%20ethical%20aspects%20of%20organ%20donation%2C%20the%20initiative%20is%20promoting%20awareness%2C%20helping%20people%20make%20informed%20decisions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Anika%20textures%20this%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20myths%20and%20conditioning%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20organ%20transplant.%20We%20work%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20NOTTO%20(National%20Organ%20%26amp%3B%20Tissue%20Transplant%20Organisation).%20The%20data%20of%20anyone%20who%20registers%20with%20us%20goes%20to%20the%20government%20system.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been%20very%20accountable.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20process%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20want%20to%20sign%20up%20to%20be%20an%20organ%20donor%2C%20I%20can%20go%20on%20the%20ORGAN%20India%20website%20and%20express%20my%20intent%20to%20donate%20my%20organs.%20Once%20I%20fill%20in%20the%20details%2C%20it%20goes%20into%20the%20system.%20Once%20you%20are%20registered%20as%20an%20organ%20donor%2C%20you%20talk%20to%20your%20family%20and%20tell%20them%20about%20your%20wish%20to%20have%20your%20organs%20donated%20in%20the%20case%20you%20are%20ever%20brain-dead.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20by%20signing%20up%20to%20become%20a%20donor%2C%20you%20are%20helping%20people%20like%20Varun%20get%20a%20new%20lease%20on%20life.%20In%20his%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20getting%20the%20transplant%20was%20like%20a%20new%20chapter%20beginning.%20I%20closed%20the%20old%20book%2C%20and%20the%20transplant%20helped%20me%20write%20a%20new%20one.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%20Deepa%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsci-tech%2Fhealth%2Forgan-transplants-hit-by-fund-constraints-and-infrastructural-deficiencies-report%2Farticle69724663.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInfrastructure%20deficiencies%2C%20low%20funds%20affecting%20organ%20transplants%20in%20India%3A%20report%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20S%20Vijay%20Kumar%2C%20published%20on%2023%20June%202025.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwtg2025.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWorld%20Transplant%20Games.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755527400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-4-1755520798.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D488510%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Diagnosed%20with%20Chronic%20Kidney%20Disease%20(CKD)%20at%20the%20age%20of%2015%2C%20Varun%20Anand%20found%20his%20calling%20in%20sports.%20This%20is%20a%20case%20in%20